Kipi-plugins 3.0.0-beta3 - Release date: 2012/11/04
------------------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES:

General : New tool to export Collection to DLNA device.
General : New tool to make video slideshow.
General : Port all plugins to KDE XML-GUI framework.

